    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Thus, the problem occurs *only* when level=0. Hmm, that sounds familiar. Indeed, a simple `a.sort_index??` already reveals the culprit:\r\n\r\n```\r\nif level:\r\n   [..]\r\n```\r\nIn other words, level=0 is handled in the same way as level=None, which means that all levels are sorted...\r\n\r\nThe solution seems simple:\r\n```\r\nif level is not None:\r\n   [..]\r\n```\r\n\r\n"
